&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;TextRun SCXW121039729 BCX0&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun SCXW121039729 BCX0&quot;&gt;Inventory Management&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;TextRun SCXW121039729 BCX0&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun SCXW121039729 BCX0&quot;&gt;:&amp;nbsp;Receive, store, and organize&amp;nbsp;inventory in the warehouse. Track inventory levels and report any discrepancies.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
